sections.heading: Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1997, ch. 21, § 1 repealed 11-12-1 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1987, ch. 239, § 1, relating to the Interstate Compact on Agricultural Grain Marketing, effective June 20, 1997. For provisions of former section,seethe 1996 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
